<paragraph blockId="5.[151,1436,1842,1939]" pageId="5" pageNumber="6">Occiput brown, face and gena yellow, frons intermediately coloured. Frons with shiny spots lateral to ocellar triangle. Antenna yellow. Clypeus and prementum yellow.</paragraph>
<caption httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/203209/files/figure.png" pageId="6" pageNumber="7" targetBox="[162,1428,187,1655]" targetPageId="6">
